{"sn46.22:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 46.22 ","sn46.22:0.2":"3. Udayivagga ","sn46.22:0.3":"Bojjhangadesanasutta ","sn46.22:1.1":"“Satta vo, bhikkhave, bojjhange desessami; ","sn46.22:1.2":"tam sunatha. ","sn46.22:1.3":"Katame ca, bhikkhave, satta bojjhanga? ","sn46.22:1.4":"Satisambojjhango …pe… upekkhasambojjhango—","sn46.22:1.5":"ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhanga”ti. ","sn46.22:1.6":"Dutiyam. "}